// Allowed-unused exceptions for VoxelVerse core pack.
//
// Anything listed here is intentionally not referenced by the rest of the
// content (blocks, items, recipes, worldgen, loot, materials). Pack Doctor
// will skip "unused" warnings for these entries.
//
// Every entry MUST include a one-line `why` field so future agents can audit
// it. No silent exceptions. If a piece of content cannot justify itself,
// delete it.
//
// IDs follow the same `core:domain/path` form Pack Doctor uses for content.
// Paths follow the on-disk path relative to the pack root (used for textures
// and other media that have no domain ID).
AllowedUnused(
    blocks: [],
    items: [],
    materials: [],
    textures: [],
    loot_tables: [],
    // Each note must be an `AllowedNote(id: "...", why: "...")` whose id is a
    // real content reference (block, item, material, texture, or loot table).
    notes: [],
)
